body:
This PR introduces new pagination types and updates our RTK Query `list` api endpoints to accept `limit` and `offset` as a part of the request.

It initially included a pagination helper, but we decided to go without it. It's fairly trivial to paginate a request without it:
```js
const [page, setPage] = useState(0);
const { data: tasksData } = useListTasksQuery({ limit: 50, offset: page * limit });
```

